---
title: Falafel Couscous with Roasted Tomatoes, Olives and Feta
description: We're celebrating veggie night with this Middle Eastern-inspired pasta! Packed with oven-roasted falafel, roasted tomatoes, briny olives, feta, and garlic-tossed cucumber, we've checked off every flavour box!
